Git Find Alias

Search for files in the repository by path.

$ [prgm]git find[/prgm] [arg-value]pattern[/arg-value]        # Find files matching pattern (case-insensitive)

Examples:
$ [prgm]git find[/prgm] [arg-value]config[/arg-value]         # Find all files with "config" in path
$ [prgm]git find[/prgm] [arg-value]\.py[/arg-value]           # Find all Python files
